{"tid":1962884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賽馬會普通科門診有員工確診武漢肺炎！無源頭！","createTime":"2020-04-07T18:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T19:02:08.000Z","uid":91914,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bddca0a753afac69886c8d05b9a53cab962953ee","tid":1962884,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T18:21:20.000Z","msg":"石湖墟賽馬會普通科門診有員工確診　北區醫院隔離治療<br />\n<br />\n石湖墟賽馬會普通科門診診所一名員工，確診感染新型肺炎，診所今日關閉一天，徹底消毒。北區醫院發言人說，該名57歲患者主要負責診所清潔工作，工作期間有穿戴個人防護裝備，上星期五開始出現咳嗽及喉嚨痛，無發燒。他過去14日內，無外遊紀錄，亦無接觸確診患者，昨晚接受深喉唾液樣本測試，證實呈陽性反應，現時在北區醫院接受隔離治療，情況穩定。診所目前未有新型肺炎確診患者的到診紀錄，正與衞生防護中心追蹤該確診員工的密切接觸者，安排檢測及跟進所需檢疫安排，並會密切監察診所職員健康情況。<br />\n<br />\n2020-04-08 01:31:54"},{"pid":"a4bab808fbd2a0ac80ded556ff55190c6277d457","tid":1962884,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T18:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae21b0bf6b34893632c751a54e67036937808af1","tid":1962884,"uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T18:22:46.000Z","msg":"大爆發啦"},{"pid":"f84fad873a65ceb0a104661f6c5895c0f0282696","tid":1962884,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T18:25:13.000Z","msg":"社區爆發啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0956f30a45dedc9ba2824e64e03b2090d959220","tid":1962884,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T18:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c73e34fa3bc02808248bfe6c609fd11727a4a28","tid":1962884,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T18:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a